s footer。v0.4.1 取代 v0.4.0 作为最新发布版本 — decision\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"decision-55a6cd5a9c29aeeb\",\n      \"type\": \"decision\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-16 08:12\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 76075,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 在 loom 项目中探索 GitHub Trending 技能集成以驱动后续工作优先级分析，并基于竞争分析和用户定位制定发布路线]\\n\\nskill 列表在 SessionStart hook 中注入，会话生命周期内不再扫描；下次会话才能读到配置变更\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/infra/loom\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"skill 列表在 SessionStart hook 中注入，会话生命周期内不再扫描； — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-4f3336ea4403ce23\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-16 06:36\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 76031,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: 在 loom 项目中探索 GitHub Trending 技能集成以驱动后续工作优先级分析；遇到 skill 系统限制]\\n\\nskill 列表在 SessionStart hook 中注入（通过 system reminder），会话生命周期内不会重新扫描\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/work/infra/loom\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"skill 列表在 SessionStart hook 中注入（通过 system reminder）， — learned\",\n      \"topic_key\": \"discovery-fd014c0844a1e2a0\",\n      \"type\": \"discovery\",\n      \"updated_at\": \"2026-05-16 06:02\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 75843,\n      \"preview\": \"[Context: Generate follow-up Codex task suggestions for remem issues around cross-project preference leakage, hook installation verification,]\\n\\n`remem context` / SessionStart output currently injects memories and preferences without explaining inclusion reasons such as branch match, recency, workstr\",\n      \"project\": \"/Users/lifcc/Desktop/code/AI/tools/remem\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"source_type\": \"memory\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"title\": \"`remem context` / SessionStart output currently injects memories and preferences without explaining — learned\",\n